[normal]4.4
[normal]              
[normal]Climate change is a global issue and given 
[normal]that the UK contribution to global greenhouse emissions i
[normal]s
[normal] &lt;1
[normal].7
[normal]% of the global total it is unlikely that, in isolation, any commercial shale production in Wales
